    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-02-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-02-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="481"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d481">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Olney</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Knight</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-02-05">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">February</hi> 5, 1896</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Report fully on present situation of Hammond and other arrested Americans. Has
                    Hammond been admitted to bail? When will trial take place?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Olney.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
